# Function execute and AI generate APIs used by execution-factory toolbox tools

### Execute function
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/agent-operator-integration/v1/function/execute
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}
x-business-domain: {{businessDomain}}

{
  "code": "def handler(event):\n    return event",
  "event": { "message": "hello" },
  "timeout": 30000
}

### AI generate python function
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/agent-operator-integration/v1/ai_generate/function/python_function_generator
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}
x-business-domain: {{businessDomain}}

{
  "query": "Generate a Python handler that uppercases the input message field."
}

### Get AI prompt template
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/agent-operator-integration/v1/ai_generate/prompt/python_function_generator
Authorization: {{token}}
x-business-domain: {{businessDomain}}
